cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.IR 

This paper focuses on deep learning for satellite imagery, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses engineering considerations and infrastructure for large-scale deep learning tasks, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper touches on data processing and modeling, which could fall under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
